Rating: 3
This dish was an instant hit with -- get this -- a crowd of young teenagers. I get requests for this appetizer again and again, and need to make a double recipe! Easy to prepare ahead, but I like to toast the bread rounds just before assembly.

Rating: 3
Quite delicious and beautiful presentation for the holidays. My one word of advice is to remember that prosciutto is very salty and parmesan or romano cheese is too. Avoid any extra salt on this appetizer.

Rating: 3
A very good snack item which can be prepared well in advance to avoid last minute hassels. Only care should be taken while storing it after it has been assembeled.